title: The Crooked Way (1949 film noir)
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0041269/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0041269/</a>

Yet another piece of noir excellence photographed by John Alton and starring John Payne. I find myself looking at this movie over and over. Its hard to imagine a darker image, or a more overcooked dialog. Almost every noir cliche you can think of is in this movie.

Directed by Robert Florey.
